    public class QueryTriplet

    This class represents a formal model of an OLAP query. It is composed of three components. The measure, the group by set (GBS) and the selection predicates...

      • addProjectionIfMoreDetailed

        public void addProjectionIfMoreDetailed(ProjectionFragment arg_p)
        Adds a projection to the query and replaces the old projection only if the given one is more detailed than the existing one. This can be used for example for drill down. It is also used for parsing MDX queries and converting them to QueryTriplet
        Parameters:
        arg_p - the projection fragment.

        public java.util.Set<EAB_Hierarchy> getHierarchyWithSelection()
